- Nadite ga na mapi.
- Našli smo, ser.

91
00:08:24,397 --> 00:08:26,636
- Onda gadajte metu.
- Da, ser.

92
00:08:26,637 --> 00:08:29,835
- Cik cak, ser?
- Šta bi VI rekli, mister?

93
00:08:29,836 --> 00:08:34,476
Ja? Pa, ne bih išao cik cak, ser.
Dajte im šansu da uspore.

94
00:08:34,477 --> 00:08:36,468
Tako je, gospodine.

95
00:08:45,421 --> 00:08:47,946
- Možete li mi to ponoviti, Radar?
- Imaš li ga?

96
00:08:48,685 --> 00:08:52,236
Procenjena kursa mete: 1-4-0.

97
00:08:52,237 --> 00:08:54,637
Brzina: 10 cvorova.

98
00:08:54,638 --> 00:08:57,644
Pravac 1-2-4.

99
